Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.53,0:03:01.57,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,I am Yukiko Hirohara, the Study of Modern Societies Club president!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.57,0:03:07.33,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,By "study of modern societies," I mean more or less the specific investigative research on all things of modern society!{gendai shyakai mo shinrabanshyou wo taishou ni chyousa kenkyuu wo suru dakuman/*"dakuman" may be "Takkuman" or Barbara Tuchman who's a historian*/}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.62,0:03:10.67,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, the modern version of classic literature!{iwaba kokugaku gendaiban desu}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.08,0:03:15.13,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,I've already heard that many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.38,0:03:20.01,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Our "study of modern societies" members are... {TLC, this line just crashes into the next}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.01,0:03:22.59,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,Not only that, but two girls and one guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.81,0:03:34.06,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's impossible.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.69,0:03:37.11,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My sister died seven years ago.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.53,0:03:40.65,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What I saw in the Crimson Night had to be an illusion.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.61,0:03:43.32,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Still, at that time...{\i0} {I remember you tsed this scene before.}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.08,0:03:48.16,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru-kun, something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.79,0:03:52.08,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,It's not good to be brooding over it. {TLC; how can she say "it" when she asked him what it is lol}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.67,0:03:55.25,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,After all, everyone's gathered here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.75,0:03:57.84,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.13,0:04:01.84,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy! I've made a lot of friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.84,0:04:03.93,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Yukiko-chan, you're incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.93,0:04:07.26,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,You've managed to survive all alone in the Crimson Night, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.26,0:04:07.85,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.85,0:04:10.81,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean that you have some kind of special power?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.81,0:04:13.14,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just a normal girl. {おんにゃの子 - can we match her speech in translation? any suggestions}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.90,0:04:17.27,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,When I snap, though, I'm scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.11,0:04:22.28,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,You're always so cheerful, Yukiko-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.15,0:04:25.28,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,Since that's my only good quality!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.62,0:04:28.70,Default,Saiko Akamine,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.03,0:04:32.08,Default,Saiko Akamine,0000,0000,0000,,Where and with whom do you fight to get injuries like these?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.96,0:04:36.50,Default,Saiko Akamine,0000,0000,0000,,You barely have enough attendance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.50,0:04:38.42,Default,Saiko Akamine,0000,0000,0000,,You're frequently late to school, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.42,0:04:40.38,Default,Saiko Akamine,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have {\i1}any{\i0} intention of graduating?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.38,0:04:44.84,Default,Takahisa Tajima,0000,0000,0000,,You're so noisy, you unmarried, no-guy woman! {sadly, i'm not good at lessening euphemism on insults just yet. any suggestions? (in other words, lower the dialogue to his level)}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.35,0:04:49.81,Default,Saiko Akamine,0000,0000,0000,,Takahisa...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.81,0:04:53.48,Default,Saiko Akamine,0000,0000,0000,,I'm {\i1}very{\i0} happy that you don't hit women.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.69,0:04:58.69,Default,Saiko Akamine,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it! Hold it right there, Takahisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.48,0:05:01.40,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,"Fragments".
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.32,0:05:06.99,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,The black knights called us "fragments".
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.99,0:05:10.41,Default,Avaritia,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have no need to answer a fragment that will soon disappear.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.91,0:05:12.95,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,What do they mean by "fragments"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.95,0:05:15.21,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Also, how many "fragments" are there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.92,0:05:17.00,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.50,0:05:19.50,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,I know one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.38,0:05:23.42,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,When I first came to the Crimson Night,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.42,0:05:26.63,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,I was saved by someone who looked like a hero of justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.89,0:05:31.06,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Did you meet her too, Yukiko-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.06,0:05:32.89,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,That person is not a "her".
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.89,0:05:34.52,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,That person is a guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.39,0:05:40.73,Default,Takahisa Tajima,0000,0000,0000,,Like I could say {\i1}anything{\i0} to her. About that world...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.73,0:05:42.40,Default,Takahisa Tajima,0000,0000,0000,,...or about this power, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.40,0:05:44.11,Default,Saiko Akamine,0000,0000,0000,,Takahisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.11,0:05:46.36,Default,Saiko Akamine,0000,0000,0000,,You're not getting away!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.78,0:05:48.20,Default,Takahisa Tajima,0000,0000,0000,,You're annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.07,0:05:51.74,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,All right! It's decided!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.74,0:05:54.29,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,For today's agenda, let's go and look for that person!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.04,0:05:58.75,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,If we decide fast, everything can be done quickly. {TLC}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.75,0:05:59.38,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.50,0:06:02.92,Default,Takahisa Tajima,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I'll just be in here for a sec...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.92,0:06:07.51,Default,Saiko Akamine,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you go, Takahisa!? Where are you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.72,0:06:11.47,Default,Takahisa Tajima,0000,0000,0000,,That was a close call.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.85,0:06:15.77,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch... What now, all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.77,0:06:17.31,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,That was mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.31,0:06:20.65,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,You're Mr. Hero of Justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.56,0:06:24.48,Default,Takahisa Tajima,0000,0000,0000,,Glasses girl? You again?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.48,0:06:25.53,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah. {is she clearing her throat or responding}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.99,0:06:28.28,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, the search is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.28,0:06:29.41,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.24,0:06:31.49,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,It's this person!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.91,0:06:37.71,Default,Takahisa Tajima,0000,0000,0000,,What a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.16,0:06:41.50,Default,Takahisa Tajima,0000,0000,0000,,For there to be this many people that can see the black moon...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.50,0:06:43.67,Default,Takahisa Tajima,0000,0000,0000,,You're Satsuki, right? {@TS: 芋県費「いもけんぴ」 = Fried Sweet Potatoes}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.17,0:06:45.17,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.92,0:06:49.01,Default,Takahisa Tajima,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really have no powers?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.93,0:06:53.85,Default,Takahisa Tajima,0000,0000,0000,,You've done pretty well surviving up to now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.85,0:06:55.10,Default,Takahisa Tajima,0000,0000,0000,,That's quite something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.10,0:06:56.02,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.47,0:06:57.73,Default,Takahisa Tajima,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.73,0:06:59.10,Default,Takahisa Tajima,0000,0000,0000,,I'm complimenting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.10,0:07:00.69,Default,Takahisa Tajima,0000,0000,0000,,You want some sweet potato chips?{or french fries shaped sugared potato chips.}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.69,0:07:01.65,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.31,0:07:03.86,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want any.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.40,0:07:05.57,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.57,0:07:07.11,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,All right then! I'll take you up on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.45,0:07:16.08,Default,Takahisa Tajima,0000,0000,0000,,So anyways...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.08,0:07:19.87,Default,Takahisa Tajima,0000,0000,0000,,There hasn't been anyone sucked into the Crimson Night that knows any details, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.87,0:07:20.83,Default,Takahisa Tajima,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I'm off.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.04,0:07:24.00,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Just a minute, Takahisa Tajima!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.00,0:07:26.46,Default,Invidia,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you going to join our study of modern societies club?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.46,0:07:28.88,Default,Takahisa Tajima,0000,0000,0000,,The weak dogs band together.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.88,0:07:31.84,Default,Takahisa Tajima,0000,0000,0000,,It's not my hobby to gather with the weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.84,0:07:33.01,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Did he say dog?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.01,0:07:34.89,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,What if the Crimson Night comes again?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.89,0:07:38.02,Default,Takahisa Tajima,0000,0000,0000,,I will manage... all by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.27,0:07:44.31,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.44,0:07:47.07,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,What a rude guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.07,0:07:48.28,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.28,0:07:50.57,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,Even though he looks like that, he's actually quite kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.90,0:07:52.74,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.20,0:07:54.53,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,He's really nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.07,0:08:00.50,Default,Takahisa Tajima,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's not disgusting. In fact, everyone would be jealous.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.23,0:08:25.06,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.06,0:08:27.98,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,If you just flail around aimlessly, you won't hit her!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.03,0:08:36.12,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,The more you hurry, the worse your swordsmanship gets!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.33,0:08:47.38,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,For what reason do you fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.04,0:08:50.42,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.59,0:08:53.51,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,...to protect Yuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.93,0:08:58.14,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,What a futile ring it has.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.56,0:09:03.06,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,They just slip through your mouth and aren't becoming flesh and blood. {by "flesh and blood" they probably mean something like "aren't becoming real" or "alive"}{yeah adverb recheck plz. prob "it isn't reflected through your actions" or this could just be a regular example of a japanese synecdoche}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.18,0:09:06.73,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Your feelings aren't turning into power.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.19,0:09:11.53,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Did you have the resolution in your sword?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.53,0:09:12.32,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Resolution?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.40,0:09:16.11,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Resolution is the acquisition of comprehension.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.66,0:09:20.33,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, you don't fully comprehend the circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.29,0:09:23.79,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,First to train is not your body but your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.91,0:09:26.42,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Change feelings into strength. {added a verb to make sense to the sentence}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.71,0:09:28.38,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Think only about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.92,0:09:30.88,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.84,0:09:36.38,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Change my feelings into strength...{\i0}{look up}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.77,0:09:44.27,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want strength.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.89,0:09:46.52,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Strength to protect Yuka.{\i0} {I know it's not literal translation but less of a sentence fragment than before}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.98,0:09:54.61,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.37,0:10:07.79,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.79,0:10:09.83,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Kakeru-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.83,0:10:11.04,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.04,0:10:13.34,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,What was I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.67,0:10:15.51,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,Let me just say that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.51,0:10:21.47,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,If we were to get into a battle right now, while trying to protect Yuka, you would die immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.47,0:10:23.56,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so... figures.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.56,0:10:26.31,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, sorry, it just slipped out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.10,0:10:28.14,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.64,0:10:29.85,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,It's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.90,0:10:32.11,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.98,0:10:36.03,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To test Kakeru-kun's resolution...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.03,0:10:39.57,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was thinking of pointing my sword at her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.83,0:10:44.24,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Those movements right now were...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.96,0:10:58.97,11eyes - Notepad,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fax-0.25\move(610,514,707,514)}The one who woke up the demon is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.31,0:11:06.60,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Yuka...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.60,0:11:07.39,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.89,0:11:10.56,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, I'm pitifully powerless,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.23,0:11:13.86,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,but I will protect you no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.65,0:11:16.36,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Don't overdo it, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.36,0:11:19.49,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any kind of powers either.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.49,0:11:24.28,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right... as long you stay by my side...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.99,0:11:29.33,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,I also think that this is for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.46,0:11:31.71,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,I want to protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.25,0:11:34.29,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,I want to turn that desire into strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.63,0:11:36.04,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.04,0:11:37.88,Default,Tadashi Teruya,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.88,0:11:39.92,Default,Tadashi Teruya,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Shiori!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.59,0:11:43.05,Default,Tadashi Teruya,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you. How are you doing, Shiori?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.05,0:11:44.55,Default,Tadashi Teruya,0000,0000,0000,,How much does it cost?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.55,0:11:47.76,Default,Shiori Momono,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't desecrate Italian. {not literal but fits her way of speech better}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.76,0:11:55.36,Default,Shiori Momono,0000,0000,0000,,But I want to be able to be in love with a demon. {TLC}{MMC: I think this is something like "I want to have a burning romance with an overseas girl versed in Latin(ラチィン？), though!"}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.36,0:11:58.03,Default,Shiori Momono,0000,0000,0000,,Please burn. Burn until you turn to ashes. {If my guess was somewhat right, add "then" at the start of this sentence plz}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.73,0:11:59.90,Default,Tadashi Teruya,0000,0000,0000,,Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.90,0:12:02.99,Default,Tadashi Teruya,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Shiori-chan, you're into the whole "ladies-first" thing, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.99,0:12:05.62,Default,Tadashi Teruya,0000,0000,0000,,I'll listen to anything you say!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.62,0:12:08.04,Default,Shiori Momono,0000,0000,0000,,Please continue on this road and...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.04,0:12:10.25,Default,Shiori Momono,0000,0000,0000,,...go turn right and die.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.12,0:12:13.04,Default,Tadashi Teruya,0000,0000,0000,,My pleasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.29,0:12:15.33,Default,Tadashi Teruya,0000,0000,0000,,Continue on this road and...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.33,0:12:16.92,Default,Tadashi Teruya,0000,0000,0000,,...turn righ-
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.79,0:12:20.26,Default,Tadashi Teruya,0000,0000,0000,,Carbonara!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.79,0:12:22.93,Default,TL Note,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}TL NOTE: Carbonara is an Italian sauce, usually with spaghetti or pasta, that has black pepper. {oh god yummy}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.26,0:12:21.88,Default,Shiori Momono,0000,0000,0000,,Arrivederci.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.88,0:12:22.93,Default,Shiori Momono,0000,0000,0000,,Good bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.68,0:12:26.80,Default,Kaori Natsuki,0000,0000,0000,,What a completely and utterly dramatic moron.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.80,0:12:27.80,Default,Kaori Natsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.81,0:12:33.94,Default,Kaori Natsuki,0000,0000,0000,,If he gets any dumber than this, who {\i1}knows{\i0} what he'll say next.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.24,0:12:45.86,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Kusakabe-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.86,0:12:46.70,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.16,0:12:48.91,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yuka went ahead already.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.99,0:12:50.99,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru-kun,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.41,0:12:53.04,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,about yesterday's practice...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.46,0:12:54.41,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.54,0:12:58.38,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,No, never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.05,0:13:09.05,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yuka...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.31,0:13:12.22,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,Good work today!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.22,0:13:15.10,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,The study of modern societies club is having a study session right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.10,0:13:17.60,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,The... modern... societies... club... study... session?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.60,0:13:20.48,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Why does Yuka-san have such large breasts...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.48,0:13:22.32,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,...even though she has such a childish figure?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.32,0:13:26.24,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, Yukiko-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.24,0:13:28.45,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,She isn't pushing them together or raising them up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.45,0:13:31.79,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,Without a push-up bra, this is a modern miracle! {push-up instead of correctional since it's the more common term}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.75,0:13:36.96,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,In such a pure school... what shameless actions!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.37,0:13:40.50,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Yukiko-chan, stop! ... I said stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.77,0:13:54.73,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,It's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.78,0:14:10.95,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,The Crimson Night...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.04,0:14:14.95,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.95,0:14:17.75,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,He's fighting... Takahisa-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.75,0:14:18.96,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.76,0:14:27.51,Default,Takahisa Tajima,0000,0000,0000,,Burn in hell! {not literal but fits his speech better}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.56,0:14:39.56,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,Takahisa-senpai is a psychic fire energy user, a pyrokinesist.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.99,0:14:52.16,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,A black knight!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.87,0:14:58.00,Default,Ira,0000,0000,0000,,You won't get away this time, "fragments"!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.37,0:15:00.33,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell {\i1}are you{\i0} all?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.67,0:15:04.38,Default,Ira,0000,0000,0000,,I have nothing to say to the walking dead. {TLC}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.38,0:15:06.46,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Questions are useless, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.46,0:15:08.72,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Yukiko-kun, I'll leave these two in your care.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.72,0:15:09.59,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.85,0:15:15.35,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Kannagiri Nagamitsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.31,0:15:20.27,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare yourself! {technically "coming" but sounds funky}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.49,0:15:32.91,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,This guy... he uses martial arts?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.45,0:15:35.66,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,He's fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.66,0:15:37.58,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Kusakabe-senpai is being pushed back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.75,0:15:48.88,Default,Avaritia,0000,0000,0000,,So it's begun, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.88,0:15:51.30,Default,Superbia,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Avaritia-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.30,0:15:53.14,Default,Avaritia,0000,0000,0000,,To have defeated Gula...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.14,0:15:54.14,Default,Avaritia,0000,0000,0000,,Those damned "fragments".
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.59,0:15:56.26,Default,Superbia,0000,0000,0000,,Please do not worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.26,0:15:58.68,Default,Superbia,0000,0000,0000,,This time, it's Ira and Invidia.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.14,0:16:02.35,Default,Superbia,0000,0000,0000,,Also, I, Superbia, will go as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.91,0:16:17.20,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.08,0:16:19.08,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.08,0:16:20.62,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Forget that, senpai is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.42,0:16:26.84,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu-senpai is in a pinch, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.67,0:16:30.84,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,If only I had some power...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.84,0:16:34.55,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe that they wished to have those powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.14,0:16:38.22,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,They had no choice but to accept their powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.81,0:16:40.72,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,It's that kind of horror. {TLC these last three lines; 1st line i think is completely wrong, 2nd and 3rd lines i have gut feeling she's referring to herself}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.02,0:16:43.06,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be going!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.32,0:16:53.53,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yukiko-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.97,0:17:23.56,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,This speed is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.73,0:17:32.86,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,What an unbelievable fighting ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.24,0:17:34.69,Default,Ira,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.12,0:17:43.12,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Yukiko-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.26,0:18:03.56,Default,Ira,0000,0000,0000,,Little girl, don't mess with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.56,0:18:05.27,Default,Ira,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.54,0:18:29.33,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Yukiko-chan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.33,0:18:31.50,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,It's like she's a different person...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.78,0:19:00.91,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,No!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.90,0:19:00.91,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yukiko!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.87,0:19:03.70,Default,Invidia,0000,0000,0000,,Ira.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.28,0:19:05.62,Default,Ira,0000,0000,0000,,So it's you, Invidia?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.04,0:19:10.54,Default,Invidia,0000,0000,0000,,I though that you'd be enough to slay the "fragments", but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.25,0:19:13.13,Default,Invidia,0000,0000,0000,,You can all just die together!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.34,0:19:17.09,Default,Takahisa Tajima,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.34,0:19:21.26,Default,Takahisa Tajima,0000,0000,0000,,The ally of justice has arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.15,0:19:35.23,Default,Invidia,0000,0000,0000,,My face is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.23,0:19:36.61,Default,Invidia,0000,0000,0000,,How {\i1}dare{\i0} you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.94,0:19:40.70,Default,Invidia,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.66,0:19:47.41,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,The Crimson Night is ending...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.25,0:19:50.71,Default,Invidia,0000,0000,0000,,I'll remember this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.08,0:19:53.79,Default,Ira,0000,0000,0000,,Next time we meet, I'll definitely...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.68,0:20:08.89,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,We made it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.43,0:20:12.77,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Yuka?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.77,0:20:15.44,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru-kun...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.74,0:20:23.36,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Ridiculous... with that severe wound...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.01,0:20:44.01,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,I've really done it, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.72,0:20:45.80,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yukiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.80,0:20:47.43,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Yukiko-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.43,0:20:50.27,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,I become like that when I take off my glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.89,0:20:52.31,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,A double personality? {"split" more common term but does it break TL?}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.81,0:20:53.73,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.73,0:20:57.48,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Superhuman fighting abilities and a terrifying blood thirst...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.48,0:20:59.40,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you obtain those abilities?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.40,0:21:04.36,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,Those, huh? I don't really want to talk about that, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.36,0:21:07.16,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, Yukiko-chan, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.62,0:21:09.62,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,She's healed!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.74,0:21:13.62,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is, I am able to regenerate!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.33,0:21:17.17,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,I have been unable to die since birth.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.76,0:21:23.26,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,You can't die?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.26,0:21:27.05,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Disgusting, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.27,0:21:39.81,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right. I'm used to it. Since a long time ago, everyone has...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.37,0:21:59.88,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,I was born in the country of Dransvania.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.88,0:22:02.63,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,There, in a millenium of blood of massacre... {TLC - で　sounds like she's referring to herself}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.63,0:22:03.84,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.63,0:22:09.39,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right, Yukiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.06,0:22:18.44,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,Now there's four people who have accepted me. Everyone here, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.40,0:22:32.83,Default,Takahisa Tajima,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's not disgusting. In fact, everyone would be jealous.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.25,0:22:38.08,Default,Takahisa Tajima,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if you get hurt, you can return back to normal afterwards.{\i0}
